#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn44.5"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn44.5:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 44 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 44 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn44.5:0.2"
msgid "1. Abyākatavagga "
msgstr "1. The Undeclared Points "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 5. Tatiyasāriputtakoṭṭhikasutta → pemasuttaṃ (bj) | sāriputta-koṭṭhiko 3 (or pema) (pts1)
msgctxt "sn44.5:0.3"
msgid "5. Tatiyasāriputtakoṭṭhikasutta "
msgstr "5. With Sāriputta and Koṭṭhita (3rd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.388, sc1
msgctxt "sn44.5:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ āyasmā ca sāriputto, āyasmā ca mahākoṭṭhiko bārāṇasiyaṃ viharanti isipatane migadāye … pe … "
msgstr "At one time Venerable Sāriputta and Venerable Mahākoṭṭhita were staying near Benares, in the deer park at Isipatana. … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn44.5:1.2"
msgid "(sāyeva pucchā.) "
msgstr "(The same down as far as:) "

msgctxt "sn44.5:1.3"
msgid "“Ko nu kho, āvuso, hetu ko paccayo, yenetaṃ abyākataṃ bhagavatā”ti? "
msgstr "“What’s the cause, reverend, what’s the reason why this has not been declared by the Buddha?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn44.5:1.4"
msgid "“Rūpe kho, āvuso, avigatarāgassa avigatacchandassa avigatapemassa avigatapipāsassa avigatapariḷāhassa avigatataṇhassa ‘hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’tipissa hoti … pe … "
msgstr "“Reverend, if you’re not rid of greed, desire, fondness, thirst, passion, and craving for form … "

msgctxt "sn44.5:1.5"
msgid "‘neva hoti na na hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’tipissa hoti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn44.5:1.6"
msgid "Vedanāya … pe … "
msgstr "feeling … "

msgctxt "sn44.5:1.7"
msgid "saññāya … pe … "
msgstr "perception … "

msgctxt "sn44.5:1.8"
msgid "saṅkhāresu … pe … "
msgstr "choices … "

msgctxt "sn44.5:1.9"
msgid "viññāṇe avigatarāgassa avigatacchandassa avigatapemassa avigatapipāsassa avigatapariḷāhassa avigatataṇhassa ‘hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’tipissa hoti … pe … "
msgstr "consciousness, you think ‘a Realized One exists after death’ … "

msgctxt "sn44.5:1.10"
msgid "‘neva hoti na na hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’tipissa hoti. "
msgstr "‘a Realized One neither exists nor doesn’t exist after death.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn44.5:1.11"
msgid "Rūpe ca kho, āvuso, vigatarāgassa … pe … "
msgstr "If you are rid of greed for form … "

msgctxt "sn44.5:1.12"
msgid "vedanāya … pe … "
msgstr "feeling … "

msgctxt "sn44.5:1.13"
msgid "saññāya … pe … "
msgstr "perception … "

msgctxt "sn44.5:1.14"
msgid "saṅkhāresu … pe … "
msgstr "choices … "

msgctxt "sn44.5:1.15"
msgid "viññāṇe vigatarāgassa vigatacchandassa vigatapemassa vigatapipāsassa vigatapariḷāhassa vigatataṇhassa ‘hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’tipissa na hoti … pe … "
msgstr "consciousness, you don’t think ‘a Realized One exists after death’ … "

msgctxt "sn44.5:1.16"
msgid "‘neva hoti na na hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’tipissa na hoti. "
msgstr "‘a Realized One neither exists nor doesn’t exist after death.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn44.5:1.17"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho, āvuso, hetu, ayaṃ paccayo, yenetaṃ abyākataṃ bhagavatā”ti. "
msgstr "This is the cause, this is the reason why this has not been declared by the Buddha.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn44.5:1.18"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
